------------------------------------------------
In case of 'npm i' problems:
 use LTS version of node (currently 6.10.3)
 npm cache verify
 npm i -g npm
Should help in case 
 ... npm\node_modules\npm\node_modules\ssri\index.js ...
 4551 error Cannot read property 'find' of undefined
